lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich scored twice in eight minutes to beat VfL Wolfsburg 2-0 on Saturday and go 11 points clear at the top of the Bundesliga as they chase an unprecedented fourth consecutive league crown.

headline.print_headline: Bayern Charge Past Hapless Wolfsburg to Extend Lead
